Event.info: OSINT - Minecraft & CS:GO Ransomware Strive For Media Attention

Attribute.value: When ransomware developers achieve huge media buzz like we saw with the PUBG Ransomware, it is not surprising to see other developers creating copycats. This is the case with two new in-development ransomware programs, if we can even call them that, for both Minecraft and Counter-Strike: Global Offensive (CS: GO).
